To Save your app or a specific widget from getting cut due to the modern adaptations of the screens like notches,etc..

How?
Just wrap what u want to be safe and Voila!!

Tip: For ur whole app to be safe wrap the scaffold :-)

Properties:
top,bottom,left,right which are all boolean and will let you specify which side u care about (if u r specific).

